headline: FirstEnergy Q3 Earnings & Sales Beat Estimates, Capital Spending Up
summary: FE's third-quarter earnings and revenues are better than expected. The company has raised its 2025 capital spending plans.

headline: CenterPoint Energy (CNP) Q3 Earnings and Revenues Beat Estimates
summary: CenterPoint (CNP) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +8.70% and +1.87%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
